\ip \bd ?Pah t…ôm…ôte naoa u?\bd* Luk t…ôm…ôte naoa u. In s…ôn…ôm…ô et…ôm tuelef kit r…ôha Iesu, m…ôto in fren w…®r kit r…ôha Pol, k…ôn t…ômaliw…ôk tep…ôt ilau Pol. In s…ôn…ôm…ô et…ôm Isrel, in Iaihlu…ô …ôm kit, m…ôto in i…ôfak kit. In tokita kit it…ôm t…ômol w…®r s…®kul. In t…ôm…ôplan w…®r nat…®mnat it…ôm k…ômotiet e n…ômeg…ôh…ôn r…ôha Iesu. In t…ôm…ôte naoa mil u: Namnus…ôn T…ôw…®r It…ôm Luk T…ôm…ôte, ne W…ôk M…®n R…ôha Aposol M…®n.  
\ip \bd ?T…ôm…ôte tatuw…®n k…ôm pah?\bd* T…ôm…ôte naoa u tatuw…®n k…ôm r…ôhan kit fren, n…ôrg…®n u Teofilas. N…®p…ôt…® n…ôr…®g u m…ôm…ô, ‚ÄúEt…ômim it…ôm tolkeike Uhg…®n.‚Äù Luk t…ôm…ôte naoa u tatuw…®n o suah u, m…ôto in t…®tun m…ôm…ô Iaihlu…ô m…®n tep…ôt okotafin.  
\ip \bd ?N…ômeg…ôh…ôn tahro nulan nian t…ôm…ôte?\bd* Net…ômim tep…ôt, n…®kilat t…ôht m…ôm…ô Luk t…ôm…ôtat…®g Rom o Sisaria nian t…ôm…ôte naoa u. E nian …ôh, namnus…ôn tep…ôt e Iesu t…ôm…®t…ôlau.  
\ip \bd ?T…ôm…ôte naoa u o naka?\bd* Luk tolkeike m…ôm…ô ot…ôte namsu kit it…ôm t…ôtuat…®p m…ôhag-…ôhag w…®r e n…ômeg…ôh…ôn r…ôha Iesu. K…ôn in t…ôm…ôghat ilat net…ôm k…ômotaliw…ôk ilat Iesu moat…ôplan w…ôk r…ôhan. Nian t…ôm…ôto r…ôk…®s r…ôhalat n…ôghat…ôn, k…ôn Luk t…ôm…ôte naoa u. In tolkeike m…ôm…ô ot…ôg…ôtun m…ôm…ô Iesu in et…ôm pahrien kit, m…ôto in t…ôm…ôsol…ôn nol…ôn rat kit. K…ôn in Uhg…®n, k…ôn in Iosmeg…ôh.  
\c 1  
