\p
\v 11 K…ôn nagelo kit r…ôha Uhg…®n tiet-ar…ôpa ron mat…ôtul …ôh e r…ôhan mat…®p ik…®n, it…ôm katuwaan nat pien-pien m…®n ik…®n.  
