\v 15 m…ôto-inu in otuwa et…ôm-iasol e n…®gan…ômt…® I…ôr…ôm…ôr…ô. K…ôn in ot…ôs…ôn…®m…ôn wain ne n…ôn…®m…ôn …ôskas…®k m…®n. K…ôn Narm…®n R…ôha Uhg…®n ot…ôrioah e n…ômeg…ôh…ôn r…ôhan, nian ot…ôtat…®g …ôh e n…ôrp…® r…ôhan mama, matuw…®n …ôm nulan nian rafin.\x - \xo 1:15 \xt Nam 6:2-3 \x*  
\v 16 K…ôn in otiuw-pa net…ôm Isrel tep…ôt kot…®t…ôl…®g-pa o I…ôr…ôm…ôr…ô, Uhg…®n r…ôhalat.  
\v 17 K…ôn in ot…ôtaup…ôn-in I…ôr…ôm…ôr…ô e narm…®n ne n…ôsan…ôn…ôn r…ôha Elaija m…ôm…ô in ot…ôuhlin n…ôt…ôl…®g…ôn r…ôha tata m…®n koat…®t…ôl…®g-p…ôn m…®n o r…ôhalat n…®sualk…ôl…ôh m…®n, k…ôn in ot…ôuhlin m…®n net…ôm koat…ôht n…ôwia Uhg…®n okotuwa m…®n e nenat…®g…ôn r…ôha net…ôm kot…ôtuat…®p. E nol…ôn …ôh, in otol n…ôpen-…ôpen…ô…ôn o n…ômeg…ôh…ôn r…ôha net…ômim o nuwam…ôn r…ôha I…ôr…ôm…ôr…ô.‚Äù\x - \xo 1:17 \xt Mal 3:1; 4:5-6; Mat 17:11-13 \x*   
\p
