\v 20 !∆èt…ôl…®g-in-tu! Nam…ôm oteko k…ôn onak…ôsag…ôt…ôn m…ôtoarus-pa nakehm n…®p…ôt…® n…ôghat…ôn u, m…ôto-inu n…ôm…ôs…ôn…ôn n…®pahrien…ôn e r…ôhak n…ôghat…ôn. In otuwa mol n…®pahrien…ôn e nian …ôtuat…®p r…ôhan.‚Äù   
