\v 3 K…ôn o n…ôghat…ôn …ôh r…ôha nafin…ôn, net…ômim rafin kot…ôk…ôike moat…®t…ôl…®g-p…ôn im…ôlat m…®n ik…®n it…ôm k…ômotaiir ik…®n m…ôm…ô okafin ilat, k…ôn k…ôte r…ôk…®s n…ôrg…®lat e naoa r…ôha kapman.  
\v 4 K…ôn Josep ne Meri k…ômiaiet e n…®t…ôn Kalili e taon kit, n…ôrg…®n u Nasaret, mian …ôp…ôh n…®t…ôn Jutia e taon kit, n…ôrg…®n u Petlehem, im…ô Kig Tef…®t aup…ôn. Ilau k…ômian ik…®n …ôh m…ôto-inu Josep in mip…® Tef…®t rat.   
\p
