\s1 Simeon t…ômehm Iesu  
\p
\v 25 K…ôn in…ôh et…ômim kit t…ôtat…®g …ôh Jerusalem, n…ôrg…®n u Simeon. R…ôhan n…ômeg…ôh…ôn in t…ôtuat…®p w…®r, k…ôn nian rafin tat…ôt…ôu-p…ôn n…ôghat…ôn r…ôha Uhg…®n. K…ôn in tat…ôsahgin nuwam…ôn r…ôha Kristo it…ôm otuwa mosmeg…ôh net…ôm Isrel lan. K…ôn Narm…®n R…ôha Uhg…®n t…ômuwa m…ôrioah e n…®kin.  
