\q1 k…ôn net…ômim okot…®l…ôs-ip…ôr r…ôham m…®n net…ôm Isrel o Iosmeg…ôh …ôh.‚Äù\x - \xo 2:32 \xt Aes 42:6; 49:6; 52:10 \x*   
\p
\v 33 K…ôn tata ne mama r…ôha suak…ôku u, narm…®lau t…ômiw…®g o n…ôghat…ôn m…®n it…ôm Simeon t…ôm…ôn lan.  
\v 34 K…ôn Simeon t…ôm…ôfak m…ôm…ô n…ôw…®r…ôn r…ôha Uhg…®n otuw…®n olau. K…ôn in t…ôm…ôn k…ôm Meri it…ôm in mama r…ôha suak…ôku m…ôm…ô, ‚ÄúOnakatehm, Uhg…®n t…ôm…®t…ôpun m…ôm…ô suak…ôku u otol m…ôm…ô net…ômim tep…ôt …ôp…ôh Isrel okoteiuaiu motorin, k…ôn tep…ôt m…®n okot…ôr. K…ôn in otuwa n…ômt…ôtin kit it…ôm net…ômim tep…ôt okot…ôghat rat lan m…ôm…ô,\x - \xo 2:34 \xt Aes 8:14; Mat 21:42; 1 Pita 2:8 \x*  
