\v 48 ‚ÄúK…ôn in tahmen …ôm e et…ômim it…ôm t…ômil…ôk…®n r…ôhan nim…ô. Aup…ôn, t…ômel n…®s…®p meiuaiu muw…®n maf…ôl w…®r k…ôpiel ap…®n …ôp…ôh l…ôhau, k…ôn mil…ôk…®n-p…ôn r…ôhan ik…®n nim…ô. Nian nuhu…ôn t…ôf…®k maiu maru…ôh muwa m…®l…ôs p…®k…ôn, m…ôto t…ôs…ôloal…ôn lan, m…ôto-inu t…ômil…ôk…®n w…®r ti…ôk…®s.  
