\p
\v 19 K…ôn e nian …ôh, mama r…ôha Iesu ne pian m…®n k…ômotuwa m…ôm…ô okotehm, m…ôto okol k…ôsotuw…®n…ôn iu…ôhk…®r motehm m…ôto-inu n…®manin net…ômim tep…ôt koat…ôtlos…®g-in.  
