\v 7 K…ôn Kig Herot Antipas u in i…ôr…ôm…ôr…ô e n…®t…ôn Kalili, in t…ôm…ôto namnus…ôn r…ôha nat…®mnat m…®n u it…ôm Iesu tatol ilat. K…ôn t…ôm…ôt…ôl…®g-in muw…®n m…®n…ôruru …ôf…ôm…ôh m…ôto-inu net…ômim neen kot…ôn m…ôm…ô Jon Baptais t…®n…ômeg…ôh m…®n,\x - \xo 9:7 \xt Mat 16:14; Mak 8:28; Luk 9:19 \x*  
\v 8 k…ôn net…ômim neen m…®n k…ômot…ôn m…ôm…ô Elaija t…®nuwa m…®n, k…ôn net…ômim neen k…ômot…ôn m…ôm…ô in ien kit r…ôha Uhg…®n aup…ôn ik…®n it…ôm t…ôm…ômeg…ôh m…®n.  
\v 9 K…ôn Herot Antipas t…ôm…ôn m…ôm…ô, ‚ÄúJon u, io en…ômohat…®p r…ôk…®s r…ôhn-kap…ô. ?M…ôto et…ômim pah u iat…ôto r…ôhan namnus…ôn?‚Äù K…ôn in t…ômateg…ôs-in Iesu m…ôm…ô ot…ôplan.\x - \xo 9:9 \xt Luk 23:8 \x*   
