\r (Mat 14:13-21; Mak 6:30-44;  //  Jon 6:1-14)  
\p
\v 10 K…ôn aposol m…®n r…ôha Iesu k…ômot…®t…ôl…®g-pa m…®n ron, k…ôn mot…ôn-ip…ôn k…ôm in nat…®mnat rafin it…ôm k…ômotol. K…ôn in t…ômit ilat motiet r…ôk…®s e net…ômim, motuw…®n …ôp…ôh e taon p…®s…®n kit m…®n, n…ôrg…®n u Petsaeta.  
\v 11 M…ôto e nian net…ômim k…ômot…ôto namnus…ôn m…ôm…ô Iesu t…®nuwa, k…ôn k…ômotuwa motuaris…®g-in ilat. K…ôn Iesu n…®kin t…ômagien …ôm nian in t…ômehm ilat, k…ôn in tat…ôg…ôtun ilat e n…ôr…ôm…ôr…ô…ôn r…ôha Uhg…®n, k…ôn matol-w…®r net…ôm koat…®m…®s kot…ômeg…ôh m…®n.   
