\p
\v 15 K…ôn net…ômim neen k…ômot…ôm…®k r…ôhalat n…®sualk…ôl…ôh m…ôtm…ôt…®g motuwa k…ôm Iesu m…ôm…ô in ot…ôl…ôh…ôu-p…ôn nelm…®n elat k…ôn m…ôfak olat. M…ôto nian r…ôhan m…®n net…ômim k…ômotehm ilat, k…ôn k…ômot…ôn-i…ôhau ilat.  
