\c 19  
\s1 Iesu ne Sakias  
\m
\v 1 K…ôn Iesu t…ômaliw…ôk muw…®n im…ô e taon u Jeriko matuw…®n m…ôm…ô otiet-ar…ôp…ôn e n…ôwtain m…ôs…®n.\fig |alt="Zaccheus in sycamore" src="LB00313B.TIF" size="span" loc="Luk 19:1-6" ref="Luk 19:1" \fig*  
\v 2 K…ôn e taon …ôh, suah kit …ôh-ik…®n, n…ôrg…®n u Sakias. In et…ôm-iasol kit r…ôha net…ôm koatos m…ôni r…ôha tak…®s, k…ôn r…ôhan naut…ô tep…ôt.  
\v 3 K…ôn in tolkeike m…ôm…ô ot…ôplan-tu m…ôm…ô Iesu in pah, m…ôto t…ôruru n…ôplan…ôn m…ôto-inu in nati…ôku…ôk…®r, k…ôn net…ômim koat…ôtulos…®g-in.  
