\v 17 K…ôn r…ôhan et…ôm-iasol t…ôm…ôn-ip…ôn k…ôm in m…ôm…ô, ‚ÄòIk iolw…ôk t…ôw…®r, n…ômol w…ôk it…ôm in t…ôw…®r. M…ôto-inu n…ômol w…ôk t…ôw…®r o nehm w…®r…ôn nat it…ôm nati…ôk…ôku, k…ôn roiu oekeg…ôhan-in m…®n ik m…ôm…ô onak…ôr…ôm…ôr…ô taon ilat ten.‚Äô\x - \xo 19:17 \xt Luk 16:10 \x*   
