\m
\v 1 Nian kit, Iesu t…ômat…ôg…ôtun net…ômim …ôp…ôh e Nim…ô R…ôha Uhg…®n, k…ôn mat…ôn-iar…ôp namnus…ôn t…ôw…®r r…ôha Uhg…®n k…ôm net…ômim. K…ôn pris asol m…®n, ne i…ôg…ôtun m…®n r…ôha Lou, ne net…ôm-iasol m…®n r…ôha noanol r…ôha Isrel k…ômotuwa kehm in,  
\v 2 k…ôn k…ômot…ôtap…ôh ron m…ôm…ô, ‚Äú?∆èn-tu k…ôm it…®mat m…ôm…ô pah t…ômeg…ôhan-in ik nakatol nat…®mnat m…®n …ôh? ?K…ôn pah t…ômeg…ôhan-in nep…ôt…ôn …ôh, Uhg…®n o et…ômim …ôm?‚Äù  
