\p
\v 9 K…ôn Iesu t…ômu…ôh nimaa n…ôghat…ôn kit k…ôm net…ômim m…ôm…ô, ‚ÄúEt…ôm-iasol kit t…ôm…ôfe nol u krep e nasum…ôn asol r…ôhan. K…ôn in t…ôm…ôl…ôh…ôu-p…ôn nasum…ôn u e nelm…® net…ômim neen, k…ôn ilat okotol w…ôk lan, k…ôn nian r…ôha n…ôul…ôk-in…ôn, okotos-ip…ôn m…ôs…®n k…ôm in. K…ôn t…ômuw…®n …ôp…ôh e n…®m…ôpt…ôn p…®s…®n kit mat…®g m…®nos nian tep…ôt.\x - \xo 20:9 \xt Aes 5:1 \x*\fig |alt="Vineyard watchtower" src="LB00104B.TIF" size="col" loc="Luk 20:9-15" ref="Luk 20:9" \fig*  
\v 10 K…ôn nian krep t…ômol noan k…ôn k…®not…ômar…ôg, et…ôm-iasol in t…ômahl-ipa r…ôhan kit iolw…ôk m…ôm…ô in otuw…®n mehm net…ôm koatol w…ôk e r…ôhan nasum…ôn m…ôm…ô okot…ôhl noa krep, k…ôn motoor kos-ip…ôn r…ôha et…ôm-iasol neen. M…ôto net…ôm m…®n …ôh k…ômot…ôtul motaht iolw…ôk …ôh, k…ôn motahl-ip…ôn t…®t…ôl…®g m…ôsot…ômki-p…ôn…ôn noa krep neen ne k…ôm in.  
\v 11 K…ôn et…ôm-iasol t…ômahl-ipa m…®n r…ôhan kit iolw…ôk m…®n. K…ôn ilat kotaht m…®n, motol naul…®s…ôn rat k…ôm in, k…ôn motahl-ip…ôn t…®t…ôl…®g m…ôsot…ômki-p…ôn…ôn noa krep neen ne k…ôm in.  
\v 12 K…ôn in tahl-ip…ôn m…®n kit m…®n, k…ôn ilat k…ômoatoh katoh kos-ip…ôn n…®m…ôg…ôm k…ôm in, k…ôn motahl-iar…ôp.   
\p
\v 13 ‚ÄúK…ôn et…ôm-iasol r…ôha nasum…ôn t…ôm…ô, ‚Äò?Ekol naka …ôh-roiu? T…ôw…®r m…ôm…ô ekahl-ip…ôn n…ôt…®k …ôtuat…®p it…ôm iakolkeike p…®k, ok…ôm-naka ilat okot…®siai-in.‚Äô K…ôn in t…ômahl-ip…ôn.   
