\p K…ôn nian net…ôm k…ômoat…ôt…ôl…®g-in in k…ômot…ôto n…ôghat…ôn …ôh, k…ômot…ôn m…ôm…ô, ‚Äú!P…ôs okol k…ôsol ag…®n-…ôh…ôn nat …ôh!‚Äù   
\p
