\p
\v 19 K…ôn i…ôg…ôtun m…®n r…ôha Lou, ne pris asol m…®n k…ômot…®tun m…ôm…ô nimaa n…ôghat…ôn r…ôhan tat…ôn ilat, k…ôn tol n…ôhlan, k…ômoateg…ôs-in suat…®p m…ôm…ô okotask…ôl…®m u…ôhai …ôm, k…®l…ôs-ip…ôn e kalapus, m…ôto k…®noat…ôgin net…ômim, k…ôn motap…ôs.   
