\p
\v 13 K…ôn Pailat t…ômaun-in pris asol m…®n, ne net…ôm-iasol r…ôha net…ôm Isrel, ne net…ômim rafin, k…ôn ilat rafin k…ômotuwa kiti…ôh.  
\v 14 K…ôn in t…ôm…ôn-ip…ôn k…ôm ilat m…ôm…ô, ‚ÄúSuah u, n…ômot…®l…ôs motuwa t…ôtul e n…®gan…ômt…ôk, k…ôn n…ômot…ôn m…ôm…ô tat…ôuhlin n…ôt…ôl…®g…ôn r…ôha net…ômim r…ôhat…ômat koatol t…®k…®m…®r k…ôm kapman. M…ôto emakil r…ôk…®s n…ôt…ôl…®g…ôn u e n…®gan…ômt…®t…ômat, k…ôn m…ôsehm…ôn m…ôm…ô t…ôm…ôtg…ôhl lou kit, k…ôn n…®p…ôgn…ômt…®n m…®n it…ôm nakoat…ôn lan t…ôsol…ôn n…®pahrien…ôn.  
\v 15 K…ôn Herot Antipas m…®n, in t…ômakil mehm m…ôm…ô nol…ôn rat kit t…ôs…ôkul-p…ôn…ôn lan. Tol n…ôhlan, in tahl-ipa tuwa m…®n o kitat, k…ôn t…ôpi…ô …ôm m…ôm…ô suah u in t…ôm…ôsol…ôn nat kit it…ôm t…ôrat m…ôm…ô in ot…®m…®s ron.  
\v 16-17 K…ôn o nat …ôh in…ôh, r…ôhak m…®n mopael okotalis …ôm, k…ôn uaris…®g kotahl-iar…ôp tatuw…®n.‚Äù\f + \fr 23:16-17 \ft E kopi oas m…®n neen r…ôha Niutesteman it…ôm k…ôm…ôte e n…ôghat…ôn Kris aup…ôn, kat…®lp…®n n…ôghat…ôn kit m…®n ik…®n-u tat…ôn m…ôm…ô, ‚ÄúE nian r…ôha lafet r…ôha Nuhagego-in…ôn, Pailat in ot…ôk…ôike mahl-iar…ôp r…ôhalat kit et…ômim otiet e kalapus.‚Äù\f*   
\p
\v 18 M…ôto ilat rafin k…ômotag…ôt …ôf…ôm…ôh moat…ôn m…ôm…ô, ‚Äú!Ot…®l…ôs-iar…ôp suah un k…ôn kohamnu! !M…ôto ahl-iar…ôp Parapas tuwa mehm it…®mat!‚Äù  
\v 19 (Suah u Parapas, k…ôm…®l…ôs-ip…ôn e kalapus m…ôto-inu in t…ômol net…ômim kot…ôluag…®n o kapman e taon …ôh, k…ôn in iohamnu it…ôm.)   
