\r (Mat 27:32-44; Mak 15:21-32;  //  Jon 19:17-27)  
\p
\v 26 K…ôn nian mopael m…®n k…ômotit Iesu motiet e taon, k…ôn k…ômot…ôplan et…ôm Saerin kit, n…ôrg…®n u Saimon. In t…ôm…®s…®-p…ôn is…ôu maliw…ôk matuwa e taon. K…ôn k…ômotask…ôl…®m mot…ôl…ôh…ôu-p…ôr n…®g k…ôluau r…ôha Iesu e nuweg…®n m…ôm…ô ot…®l…ôs, k…ôn mot…ôn-ip…ôn m…ôm…ô ot…ôt…ôu-p…ôn Iesu.\fig |alt="three crosses on hill outside city wall" src="HK00326B.TIF" size="span" loc="Luk 23:26-43" ref="Luk 23:26" \fig*  
\v 27 K…ôn n…®manin net…ômim tep…ôt k…ômotaliw…ôk katuaris…®g-in Iesu e suat…®p, k…ôn n…®p…®tan tep…ôt m…®n koatuaris…®g-in ilat, koatas…ôk moat…ôun-…ôun o Iesu.  
