\v 33 K…ôn k…ômotuwa ik…®n kit, n…ôrg…®n u Louip…®l-uip…®l. Ik…®n …ôh, k…ômot…ôtu-p…ôr Iesu e n…®g k…ôm…ôluau. K…ôn k…ômot…ôtu-p…ôr i…ôtg…ôhl lou mil …ôh-ik…®n, kit e n…®kal…® Iesu mat…®p, k…ôn kit e n…®kal…®n mol.  
\v 34 K…ôn Iesu t…ôm…ô, ‚ÄúTata. Aluin r…ôhalat nol…ôn rat m…®n it…ôm koatol k…ôm io, k…ôn m…ôsalp…®n…ôn, m…ôto-inu k…ôsot…®tun…ôn nat naka it…ôm koatol.‚Äù K…ôn k…ômotoor r…ôhan nat…®mnat moaturin taes ron.\x - \xo 23:34 \xt Sam 22:18; Aes 53:12 \x*   
\p
\v 35 K…ôn net…ôm m…®n u koat…ôtul …ôh-ik…®n, moatehm nat…®mnat m…®n u, m…ôto et…ôm-iasol m…®n r…ôha noanol r…ôha Isrel kotalah …ôsan e Iesu moat…ôn m…ôm…ô, ‚Äú!In t…ômosmeg…ôh net…ômim tep…ôt r…ôk…®s. M…ôto ok…ôm…ô in Kristo it…ôm Uhg…®n t…ôm…ôn m…ôm…ô otahl-ipa, k…ôn in Et…ôm Uhg…®n T…ôm…®t…ôpun, k…ôn p…ôs in otosmeg…ôh at…®p in!‚Äù\x - \xo 23:35 \xt Sam 22:7-8 \x*   
\p
\v 36 K…ôn mopael m…®n, ilat m…®n koat…ôghat …ôsan e Iesu, k…ôn motuwa iu…ôhk…®r ron moat…ôtap…ôh m…ôm…ô in tolkeike wain u it…ôm tag…®n,\f + \fr 23:36 \ft Wain u it…ôm tag…®n, in n…ôn…®m…ôn r…ôha ian-rat m…®n.\f*\x - \xo 23:36 \xt Sam 69:21 \x*  
\v 37 moat…ôn m…ôm…ô, ‚Äú!Ok…ôm…ô n…®pahrien…ôn ik kig r…ôha noanol m…®n r…ôha Isrel, osmeg…ôh at…®p ik …ôh-roiu!‚Äù   
\p
\v 38 K…ôn n…ôghat…ôn kit …ôh-ik…®n k…ôm…ôte k…ôtu-p…ôr e r…ôhn-kap…ô n…®g k…ôluau, tat…ôn m…ôm…ô, \sc Inu kig r…ôha net…ôm Isrel\sc*.   
\p
\v 39 K…ôn i…ôtg…ôhl lou mil kit it…ôm kat…ôkul-p…ôr e n…®g k…ôluau, in tat…ôghat rat e Iesu, mat…ôn m…ôm…ô, ‚Äú!Ei! ?Ik Kristo it…ôm Uhg…®n t…ôm…ôn m…ôm…ô otahl-ipa, o k…ôp? !Ok…ôm…ô tol mihin, osmeg…ôh ik k…ôn mosmeg…ôh m…®n it…®mlau!‚Äù   
