\p
\v 50-51 K…ôn et…ôm Aramatia kit …ôh-ik…®n, n…ôrg…®n u Josep. Aramatia in taon kit r…ôha Isrel, k…ôn suah …ôh in et…ômim kit r…ôha kaonsel r…ôha net…ôm Isrel. In et…ôm t…ôw…®r, r…ôhan n…ômeg…ôh…ôn t…ôtuat…®p, k…ôn in et…ômim kit t…ômat…ôsahgin m…ôm…ô ot…ôplan n…ôr…ôm…ôr…ô…ôn r…ôha Uhg…®n. K…ôn in t…ôm…ôseg…ôhan…ôn e n…ôghat…ôn r…ôha kaonsel it…ôm k…ômoateg…ôhan-in Iesu m…ôm…ô okoh.  
\v 52 K…ôn in t…ômuw…®n mehm Pailat m…ôtap…ôh ron m…ôm…ô oteg…ôhan-in n…®p…ôt…® Iesu tos.  
\v 53 K…ôn Josep t…ômuw…®n m…®l…ôs-i…ôhau n…®p…ôt…® Iesu e n…®g k…ôm…ôluau, mos muwa malpin e n…®m…ôhan w…®r kit, n…ôrg…®n u linen. K…ôn t…ôm…®l…ôs muw…®n m…ôl…ôh…ôu-p…ôn e n…®p…ôg k…ôpiel it…ôm k…®n…ôm…ôte r…ôk…®s o nol…ôn suw…®t ik…®n, m…ôto k…ôs…®t…ôn…®m…ôn …ôh suah kit ik…®n.  
\v 54 In …ôh e nian r…ôha noanol m…®n r…ôha Isrel it…ôm koatol …ôpen-…ôpen…ô lan o nian r…ôha Sapat, k…ôn iu…ôhk…®r Sapat t…ôtuoun.   
\p
\v 55 K…ôn n…®p…®tan it…ôm k…ômot…®s…®-p…ôn Kalili k…ômotuaris…®g-in Iesu, k…ômot…ôt…ôu-p…ôn suah un, motuw…®n mot…ôplan n…®p…ôg k…ôpiel, k…ôn mot…ôplan nol…ôn it…ôm in tat…ôl…ôh…ôu-p…ôn min Iesu ik…®n.  
